In recent years, farm-based farming by Heilongjiang has played a leading role in the demonstration of modern, large-scale agricultural “carriers”, leading to the initial establishment of modern agro-industrial systems dominated by scale farming, standardized production and industrialization.
On the outskirts of Friendship County, there is a 350,000 square metre farm machine exhibition park.
More than 140 agricultural tools have been introduced and used by Heilongjiang farmers over the years.
