It's a straight line.
Zheng Wangai was established in the city of Zhengzhou, Henan Province, on a new route from the city of Pyeongshan in the south-west, the city of Namyang, and the city of Jaeyang in Hubei Province to Huangzhou in Chongqing City, approximately 818 km long, designed to speed 350 km/hour and about 184 km inside Chongqing territory.
